messages.content: 9-1-1, what's your emergency?
Hi, um, I think I may have found possibly a body in a trash bag.
Okay, where are you?
And then there's a girl missing from Ohio.
Yeah, where are you? And what makes you think it's possibly her?
Um, well, I can smell something. I was doing some paperwork, turned around, and smelled it.
I could see, like, you can tell there was a smell coming from the bag.
The bag looked unusual, so I decided to take a closer look.
There's a trash bag back there, and the only reason I checked is because it seemed out of place.
So I decided to poke it a bit to see what was inside.
I couldn't tell what it was at first, but then I saw a Hooters shirt. I could read 'Hooters' across the shirt.
Okay. And is there definitely more than just clothing in there?
Oh, yeah. At first it seemed like there might be something else, like a turtle or something.
But when I saw the shirt material, I knew I should call.
Okay, and the smell is really bad, right?
Yeah, yeah.
And your name is?
It's [Name].
Alright. We'll get a deputy right out to you, okay?
Okay. Thank you.
Bye-bye.
